      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杜丽娘上。",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00002",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 2,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "蓦地游春转，小试宜春面。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00003",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 3,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "春吓春！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00004",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 4,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "得和你两留连，春支如何遣？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00005",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 5,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "咳，恁般天气，好困人也！",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00006",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 6,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山坡羊",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "没乱里春情难遣，蓦地里怀人幽怨。则为俺生小婵娟，拣名门一例一例里神仙眷。甚良缘，把青春抛的远。俺的睡情谁见？则索因循腼腆。想幽梦谁边，和春光暗流转？迁延，这衷怀哪处言？淹煎，泼残生除问天。",
      "text_length": 94
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00007",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 7,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖万年欢〗。杜丽娘入梦。花神引杜丽娘、柳梦梅同上，相见。〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 34
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00008",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 8,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "吓姐姐！小生哪一处不寻到，却在这里。恰好在花园内，折得垂柳半枝。姐姐，你既淹通诗书，何不作诗一首，以赏此柳枝乎？",
      "text_length": 56
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00009",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 9,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "那生素昧平生，因何到此？",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00010",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 10,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "姐姐，咱一片闲情，爱煞你哩！",
      "text_length": 14
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00011",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 11,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山桃红",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "则为你如花美眷，似水流年，是答儿闲寻遍？在幽闺自怜。",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00012",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 12,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "姐姐，和你那答儿讲话去。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00013",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 13,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "哪里去？",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00014",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 14,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "哪！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00015",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 15,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 1,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山桃红",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "转过这芍药栏前，紧靠着湖山石边。和你把领扣松，衣带宽，袖梢儿揾着牙儿苫，也。则待你忍耐温存一晌眠。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00016",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 16,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同山桃红",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅",
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "是哪处曾相见？相看俨然，早难道好处相逢无一言。⑴",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00017",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 17,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖万年欢〗。柳梦梅、杜丽娘同下。〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00018",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 18,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "内同画眉序",
      "speakers": [
        "众花神"
      ],
      "text": "好景艳阳天，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00019",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 19,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖一枝花〗。众花神同上，站定。〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00020",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 20,
      "seq_in_scene": 20,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同画眉序",
      "speakers": [
        "众花神"
      ],
      "text": "万紫千红尽开遍。满雕栏宝砌，云簇霞鲜。督春工珍护芳菲，免被那晓风吹颤，使佳人才子少系念，梦儿中也十分欢忭。",
      "text_length": 53
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00021",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 21,
      "seq_in_scene": 21,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖节节高〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00022",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 22,
      "seq_in_scene": 22,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同滴溜子",
      "speakers": [
        "众花神"
      ],
      "text": "湖山畔，湖山畔，云蒸霞焕。雕栏外，雕栏外，红翻翠骈。惹下蜂愁蝶恋，三生锦绣般非因梦幻。一阵香风，送到林园。及时的，及时的，去游春，莫迟慢。怕罡风，怕罡风，吹得了花零乱，辜负了好春光，徒唤枉然，徒唤了枉然。",
      "text_length": 102
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00023",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 23,
      "seq_in_scene": 23,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖节节高〗。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00024",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 24,
      "seq_in_scene": 24,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同五般宜",
      "speakers": [
        "众花神"
      ],
      "text": "一边儿燕喃喃软又甜，一边儿莺呖呖脆又圆。一边蝶飞舞，往来在花丛间，一边蜂儿逐趁，眼花撩乱。一边红桃呈艳，一边绿柳垂线。似这等万紫千红齐装点，大地上景物多灿烂！",
      "text_length": 79
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00025",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 25,
      "seq_in_scene": 25,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "〖万年欢〗。众花神同下。柳梦梅、杜丽娘同上。〖曲牌收〗。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00026",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 26,
      "seq_in_scene": 26,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山桃红",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "这一霎天留人便，草藉花眠。则把云鬟点，红松翠偏。见了你紧相偎，慢厮连，恨不得肉儿般和你团成片，也。逗的个日下胭脂雨上鲜。",
      "text_length": 60
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00027",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 27,
      "seq_in_scene": 27,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "妙！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00028",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 28,
      "seq_in_scene": 28,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山桃红",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "我欲去还留恋，相看俨然，早难道好处相逢无一言。⑵",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00029",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 29,
      "seq_in_scene": 29,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "姐姐，你身子乏了，将息片时，小生去也。正是：",
      "text_length": 22
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00030",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 30,
      "seq_in_scene": 30,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "行来春色三分雨，",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00031",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 31,
      "seq_in_scene": 31,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "秀才！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00032",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 32,
      "seq_in_scene": 32,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "在！妙吓！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00033",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 33,
      "seq_in_scene": 33,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "睡去巫山一片云。",
      "text_length": 8
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00034",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 34,
      "seq_in_scene": 34,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "柳梦梅下。杜母上。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00035",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 35,
      "seq_in_scene": 35,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "夫婿坐黄堂，娇娃立绣窗。怪她裙衩上，花鸟绣双双。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00036",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 36,
      "seq_in_scene": 36,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "我儿原来昼眠在此。我儿！我儿！",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00037",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 37,
      "seq_in_scene": 37,
      "page_no": 2,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "秀……",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00038",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 38,
      "seq_in_scene": 38,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "儿吓！娘在此。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00039",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 39,
      "seq_in_scene": 39,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "原来是母亲。母亲万福。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00040",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 40,
      "seq_in_scene": 40,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "罢了。你方才说什么“秀”？",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00041",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 41,
      "seq_in_scene": 41,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "吖，孩儿剌绣才罢。",
      "text_length": 9
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00042",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 42,
      "seq_in_scene": 42,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "为何昼眠在此？",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00043",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 43,
      "seq_in_scene": 43,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "告母亲知道：适才花园中游玩回来，不觉身子困倦，少睡片时。不知母亲到来，有失迎接，望母亲恕罪。",
      "text_length": 46
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00044",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 44,
      "seq_in_scene": 44,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "怎么不到学堂中去看书？",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00045",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 45,
      "seq_in_scene": 45,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "先生不在，且自消停。",
      "text_length": 10
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00046",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 46,
      "seq_in_scene": 46,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "儿吓，花园冷静，少去闲游。",
      "text_length": 13
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00047",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 47,
      "seq_in_scene": 47,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "谨依母亲慈训。",
      "text_length": 7
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00048",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 48,
      "seq_in_scene": 48,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "女儿家长成了，就有许多情态。且自由她，我去了。正是：",
      "text_length": 26
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00049",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 49,
      "seq_in_scene": 49,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "宛转随儿女，",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00050",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 50,
      "seq_in_scene": 50,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "孩儿送母亲。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00051",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 51,
      "seq_in_scene": 51,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "罢了。",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00052",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 52,
      "seq_in_scene": 52,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "杜母"
      ],
      "text": "辛勤做老娘。",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00053",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 53,
      "seq_in_scene": 53,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杜母下。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00054",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 54,
      "seq_in_scene": 54,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "娘吓！你教孩儿看书，不知哪一种书才消得我闷怀吓！",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00055",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 55,
      "seq_in_scene": 55,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "绵搭絮",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "雨香云片，才到梦儿边。无奈高堂，唤醒纱窗睡不便。泼新鲜，俺的冷汗粘煎，闪的俺心悠步軃，意软鬟偏。不争多费尽神情，坐起谁忺，则待去眠。",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00056",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 56,
      "seq_in_scene": 56,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "春香上。",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00057",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 57,
      "seq_in_scene": 57,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "recitation",
      "mode_label": "念",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "花深留翠钿，茶熟带红妆。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00058",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 58,
      "seq_in_scene": 58,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "春香"
      ],
      "text": "啊小姐，绣被已熏，请小姐安睡去吧。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00059",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 59,
      "seq_in_scene": 59,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "搀我来！",
      "text_length": 4
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00060",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 60,
      "seq_in_scene": 60,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "困春心，游赏倦，也不索香薰绣被眠。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00061",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 61,
      "seq_in_scene": 61,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "春吓！",
      "text_length": 3
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00062",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 62,
      "seq_in_scene": 62,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "尾声",
      "speakers": [
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "有心情那梦儿还去不远。",
      "text_length": 11
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00063",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 63,
      "seq_in_scene": 63,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "杜丽娘下。——————————⑴〖山桃红〗改词。",
      "text_length": 24
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00064",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 64,
      "seq_in_scene": 64,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山桃红",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "转过这芍药栏前，紧靠着湖山石边。我和你手相携，行并肩，眼梢儿待共春情展，也。则怕那花气熏人醉欲眠。",
      "text_length": 49
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00065",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 65,
      "seq_in_scene": 65,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "同山桃红",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅",
        "杜丽娘"
      ],
      "text": "是哪处曾相见？相看俨然，早难道好处相逢无一言。⑵〖山桃红〗改词。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00066",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 66,
      "seq_in_scene": 66,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "other_vocal",
      "mode_label": "山桃红",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "这一霎天留人便，草藉花眠，则把云鬟点，红松翠偏。见了你紧相随，慢厮连，一似那好花连理开成片，也。逗得个柳眼梅心别样妍。",
      "text_length": 59
    },
    {
      "event_id": "70902110_e00067",
      "play_id": "70902110",
      "scene_id": "70902110_s01",
      "scene_no": 1,
      "seq_global": 67,
      "seq_in_scene": 67,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "柳梦梅"
      ],
      "text": "妙！",
      "text_length": 2
